sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as NLP Admin
    participant UI as Training UI
    participant API as Training API
    participant DB as Training Data DB
    participant Trainer as Rasa Trainer
    participant Store as Model Storage
    participant Registry as Model Registry
    participant Rasa as Rasa Runtime

    Admin->>UI: Active bo training data
    UI->>API: POST /training-data/active
    API->>DB: Gan version ACTIVE
    Admin->>UI: Bam Train model
    UI->>API: POST /models/train
    API->>DB: Lay training data ACTIVE
    API->>Trainer: Chay rasa train
    alt Train thanh cong
        Trainer-->>API: Model artifact + metrics
        API->>Store: Luu model
        API->>Registry: Tao version READY
        API->>Rasa: Tuy chon run model moi
        Rasa-->>API: Reload OK
        API->>Registry: Cap nhat ACTIVE neu duoc phe duyet
        API-->>UI: Tra ket qua train
    else Train loi
        Trainer-->>API: Validation/training error
        API->>Registry: Cap nhat FAILED
        API-->>UI: Hien thi log loi
    end
